  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vault of Power is an autobattler stategy roguelike. Figure out your own strategy and try to conquer challenging dungeons.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mix and match powerful skills</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/99414a0de745e4f7330df29243c1964e.poster.avif?t=1743490697\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/99414a0de745e4f7330df29243c1964e.webm?t=1743490697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/99414a0de745e4f7330df29243c1964e.mp4?t=1743490697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix and match from over 50 unique spells to create your own unique build.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Engage in tough battles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/4fd9431bf8c4e60e8452e79654ab3405.poster.avif?t=1743490697\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/4fd9431bf8c4e60e8452e79654ab3405.webm?t=1743490697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/4fd9431bf8c4e60e8452e79654ab3405.mp4?t=1743490697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan and prepare before each battle. Battles play out automatically.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomized encounters, no run is the same.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gain powerful class bonuses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/6661cded42a44fa053438bac3d9ee324.poster.avif?t=1743490697\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/6661cded42a44fa053438bac3d9ee324.webm?t=1743490697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/6661cded42a44fa053438bac3d9ee324.mp4?t=1743490697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summon the dead as the Necromancer, command storms as the Druid, or cast meteors as the Mage.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vault of Power is an autobattler stategy roguelike. Figure out your own strategy and try to conquer challenging dungeons.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mix and match powerful skills</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/99414a0de745e4f7330df29243c1964e.poster.avif?t=1743490697\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/99414a0de745e4f7330df29243c1964e.webm?t=1743490697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/99414a0de745e4f7330df29243c1964e.mp4?t=1743490697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix and match from over 50 unique spells to create your own unique build.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Engage in tough battles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/4fd9431bf8c4e60e8452e79654ab3405.poster.avif?t=1743490697\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/4fd9431bf8c4e60e8452e79654ab3405.webm?t=1743490697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/4fd9431bf8c4e60e8452e79654ab3405.mp4?t=1743490697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan and prepare before each battle. Battles play out automatically.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomized encounters, no run is the same.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gain powerful class bonuses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/6661cded42a44fa053438bac3d9ee324.poster.avif?t=1743490697\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/6661cded42a44fa053438bac3d9ee324.webm?t=1743490697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515050/extras/6661cded42a44fa053438bac3d9ee324.mp4?t=1743490697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summon the dead as the Necromancer, command storms as the Druid, or cast meteors as the Mage.</p></li></ul>",
